    <item>
      <title>核大国将继续增强核弹头数量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/nuclear-powers-set-to-continue-boosting-operational-warheads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯德哥尔摩国际和平研究所称，未来几年，部署在导弹和飞机上的核弹头数量可能还会进一步增加，这种现象“极为令人担忧”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/nuclear-powers-set-to-continue-boosting-operational-warheads</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 22:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美韩日将在就职典礼前确定安全关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/us-south-korea-japan-to-lock-in-security-ties-before-inauguration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国、韩国和日本将签署一项协议，正式确立三国针对朝鲜核武器威胁的安全伙伴关系，在美国明年 1 月举行下一任总统就职典礼之前巩固三国关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/us-south-korea-japan-to-lock-in-security-ties-before-inauguration</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国保皇派与他信展开新一轮对决 押下高风险赌注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/thai-royalists-make-risky-bet-in-fresh-showdown-with-thaksin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年 8 月，泰国前领导人他信·西那瓦与曾发动政变推翻他的保皇派达成协议，结束了 15 年的流亡生涯，返回祖国。现在，这种权宜之计面临破裂的风险，可能会引发更多政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/thai-royalists-make-risky-bet-in-fresh-showdown-with-thaksin</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>祖马党赢得南非议会席位，挑战选举结果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/south-african-elections-zuma-party-takes-up-seats-in-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非前总统雅各布·祖马领导的政党将结束对议会的抵制，并夺取上个月选举中赢得的席位，同时对投票结果提出质疑。]]></description>
